    "longBusinessSummary": "Mutakamela Insurance Company provides insurance products and solution in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. It operates through Motor, Health care, Property and Casualty, and Protection and Saving segments. The company offers accident, fire or theft, and third-party liability motor insurance; medical cover to policyholders; group retirement products; and protection and saving products to individuals and corporate institutions. It also provides engineering insurance for builders' risks, construction, mechanical, electrical, electronic, machinery breakdown, and other; property accidental physical loss or damage, fire and allied perils, and related losses; and marine, credit, fidelity guarantee, and liability insurance products, as well as burglary and money insurance solutions. The company was formerly known as Allianz Saudi Fransi Cooperative Insurance Company and changed its name to Mutakamela Insurance Company in November 2024. Mutakamela Insurance Company was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Riyadh, the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. Mutakamela Insurance Company is a subsidiary of Abu Dhabi National Insurance Company PJSC.",
